rComments: He is so boring but provides good feedback on graded material and is very accessible after class.
Lectures are boring but he is an easy marker.

Although this professor may not be as good at lecturing as others, his heart is in the right place. He is super caring and will answer your questions with detail if youre patient. The course itself is very dry and needs a lot of memorizing, so he cant be completely blamed if its not interesting. Extremely nice guy!

He is a very nice person, but is not an effective lecturer. He basically lectures to the chalk board and does not make the class interactive like other professors. If you are in his section, it would be wise for you to attend a different professors section, yet still attend his for participation marks

Extremely monotone and lack lustre. Seems as though he puts minimal effort into his lectures, his slides, and does not provide a learning environment that students can thrive in. The lectures were torturous to sit through, but required for participation marks. Would not recommend this prof at all.

His teaching style is very ineffective. Funny how he teaches about being an effect leader through communication and respect in the workplace, yet he does not follow any of those topics. I believe he does not communicate with the other professors since his slides given are VERY different and dull. He sighs very loudly in class which is disrespectful

This professor is horrible when it comes to lecturing, answering questions, and resolving problems. Recently had a complaint that group members were not doing any work for the project and said there was nothing he could do, even though the syllabus explicitly states that he must lower their project grade. Did not even give practice midterms.

I question the logic behind whoever hired this professor. He is very useless compared to other professors and does not provide his students with all the resources that other students are given. All his students are at a disadvantage considering the midterm is common. STAY AWAY FROM HIM.
